{"tid":910402,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★男子石硤尾邨遇劫　遭10人撳地圍毆搶iPhone8","createTime":"2018-11-21T07:10:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-21T07:45:10.000Z","uid":19454,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"06a2a96a4a0bc4267fde4b99c585da53bd0d8fc3","tid":910402,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T07:10:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181121/photo/bkn-20181121010556464-1121_00822_001_01b.jpg?20181121110432\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181121%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181121010556464-1121_00822_001_01b.jpg%3F20181121110432&h=ab0f8a51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一名姓曾（27歲）愛貓男子，昨日(20日)深夜11時許，偕女友人同到石硤尾邨美如樓外餵流浪貓，期間女友人因事先行離開。未幾，他報稱突有<span style=\"color: red;\">約10名年約20歲男子衝出</span>，二話不說向他圍毆，他被人將頭部按在地上，再拳打腳踢，價值約9000港元的iPhone8手機於混亂間跌落地上，即被人乘機搶走，亦有人搶去其眼鏡，眾人得手後逃去。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181121/bkn-20181121010556464-1121_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181121%2Fbkn-20181121010556464-1121_00822_001.html&d=bSqfC3QsucwX7RxuYEpRAUbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=1f856ce7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181121/bkn-20181121010556464-1121_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"fcf7f8ad4626aeef891876c226ad137a2d59f5f7","tid":910402,"uid":19454,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T07:12:13.000Z","msg":"似尋仇多<br />\n<br />\n搶iphone 8<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12f09c8e15b4be8b5f0b82df74423736209844c8","tid":910402,"uid":42367,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T07:13:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\